{"tid":44481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐西蘭沙灘舉辦 Free the Nipple 大陸遊客色迷迷拍照","createTime":"2016-12-18T10:18:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T11:04:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c64e4ff02d736778b4bbf92ad23605d1f1439ea","tid":44481,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple01.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Ffree_nipple01.jpg&d=rSimjt9jxvFkBhG6WqqG1ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=98752d5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple01.jpg</a> <br />\n<br />\n來自紐西蘭的大學生 Grace Blundell (上圖右) 早前在當地沙灘 Mission Bay 舉行「Free the Nipple」，這是近年性別平權運動中較受注目的一種，抗議人們普遍對於男性及女性乳頭的差別對待，常見的情況就是當女性「露兩點」照片出現在 Instagram 或 Facebook 上，即使內容不含色情意識，也會遭檢舉及刪除。 <br />\n<br />\n主辦人表示，她希望女性能夠自由選擇自己喜歡 / 覺得舒服的衣裳，而不是經常被人與性掛勾，或遭人指指點點。不過當活動舉辦時，還是難免吸引了一批沙灘旅客前來「觀光」及拿起相機拍照。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple02.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Ffree_nipple02.jpg&d=rSimjt9jxvFkBhG6WqqG1ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=1b1cfd99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple02.jpg</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGrace Blundell 表示，這個行動其實就是希望讓女性上空變得「平常化」，即是我們看到男人露兩點也不會特地去拍照吧？但是當遇到有人在這過程中不斷拍照，甚至顯然有些人是「帶著有色眼鏡去拍」的時候，那依然令人不舒服，但如果去指摘他們呢，那又正好與自己所宣導的主張相矛盾。 <br />\n<br />\n活動進行時，也有人問她「為甚麼不索性全裸」，而女生的回答是「為甚麼你不去問那裏的半裸男呢？」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple03.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Ffree_nipple03.jpg&d=rSimjt9jxvFkBhG6WqqG1ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=65c44dd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple03.jpg</a> <br />\n<br />\n據其所述，在 1930 年代以前，男人一樣是不允許公開地展示乳頭的，但是他們在經過抗議後，慢慢社會就接受男性可以無上裝，甚至習以為常，那麼女性是否可以獲得相同的權利？抑或女性的乳頭就等於了性？"},{"pid":"041e379939f22caaf4bc221909519b135bb713b8","tid":44481,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Ffree_nipple04.jpg&h=a76d1c29&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Ffree_nipple05.jpg&h=6bc71cb7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/free_nipple06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Ffree_nipple06.jpg&h=e5481b54&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n目前來說，在網上發佈女性露點照片是很容易被歸類於色情，色情也經常被污名化，而對於較保守的中港台地區來說，更不是容易處理的議題，至少人們對於兩性平等本身就有相當大的分歧呢。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/group.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fgroup.jpg&d=rSimjt9jxvFkBhG6WqqG1ZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=23b90284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://photoblog.hk/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/group.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"38f9c54ea0004c1339583a04158ca48239672a5a","tid":44481,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"支那人係咁架啦，事無大小，乜撚都影一餐，都唔撚識尊重人既。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁講，但見到大波pink Lin 靚女我都可能會影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5da17b1b7327ca0b64e15090578a898a195462","tid":44481,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那人係咁架啦，事無大小，乜撚都影一餐，都唔撚識尊重人既。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然咁講，但見到大波pink Lin 靚女我都可能會影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都會扮支那人一齊影"},{"pid":"44e2fd707d2bd7e22bf633f164ec0949405563f5","tid":44481,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:36:10.000Z","msg":"無格圖呢"},{"pid":"aed82762f50d4634188824704384b74b6d9c1a58","tid":44481,"uid":53660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:49:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2aed139501c8703ac2c05a94bc738c7201336d80","tid":44481,"uid":30085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"認真 公眾場所比得人睇就預比人影"},{"pid":"ba78bdc3121689de3a08fa9c57460cfcc546bf1b","tid":44481,"uid":12269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"女人真係on9<br />\n唔好戴有色眼鏡？<br />\n男人見到裸女唔扯，你都驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ebd99af7ce09e4de35dde2f2014e782b2abaeb","tid":44481,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"成排人樣衰啲啫，中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實你要男女平權就接受男人真係對你粒lin有興趣啦"},{"pid":"79f443288d47bcfb8ead70827e175dd673721c3a","tid":44481,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T11:04:35.000Z","msg":"咁影好冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}